<h1>伊朗公布名为“法塔赫”的首款高超音速导弹</h1>
<p>Author: 半岛电视台</p>
<p>Publisher: Al Jazeera</p>
<p>Published Time: 2023-06-06T13:42:43</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-06-06T13:42:43</p>
